(5275, 'Better Leader, Richer Life', 'The Total Leadership approach will help you become a better leader by having a richer life and have a richer life by becoming a better leader.  Learn a practical, proven method for how to articulate your core values and vision; build trust with your most important people; and achieve "four-way wins" -- improved performance at work or in school, at home with your family, in your community, and for your self mind, body, spirit.  Its not about "work/life balance"; its about creating harmony among the different parts of your life as a leader in all of them. ', 'The Total Leadership approach will help you become a better leader by having a richer life and have a richer life by becoming a better leader.  Learn a practical, proven method for how to articulate your core values and vision; build trust with your most important people; and achieve "four-way wins" -- improved performance at work or in school, at home with your family, in your community, and for your self mind, body, spirit.  Its not about "work/life balance"; its about creating harmony among the different parts of your life as a leader in all of them. ', 'https://class.coursera.org/totalleadership-003/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=quaJcL4_XTw', '2015-02-08', 10, 'https://coursera-course-photos.s3.amazonaws.com/a4/3c21109d5211e3b1b42f3b3e379cbf/coursera_logo_17.png', 'Health & Society,Business & Management,Education,Social Sciences,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'University of Pennsylvania,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
