(99, 'Obesity: Causes and Consequences', 'Obesity is a global epidemic. As the world gets fatter, explore its impact on our health and lives, with this free online course.', 'Obesity is changing the world we live in. Across a wide range of sectors - from the food industry to clothing design - we see the impact of the worldâs growing waistline.', 'https://www.futurelearn.com/courses/obesity', 'http://view.vzaar.com/2326776.mp4', '0000-00-00', 4, 'https://ugc.futurelearn.com/uploads/images/1f/f8/regular_1ff8c595-917b-4bec-b2c6-90dd4e26cf77.jpg', 'Health & Psychology', 'FutureLearn.com', 0, 'english', 'yes', 'University of Reading', '2015-11-04 00:01:26'),
