(3464, 'The Boardroom', 'This is an advanced entrepreneurship class, designed for teams who have already started a company or are seriously thinking about starting a company.', 'This is an advanced entrepreneurship class, designed for teams who have already started a company or are seriously thinking about starting a company. We encourage teams to take this class together as much of the work will be focused on working with your board to make real progress on the most important issues in your startup. For each startup team, we will create a board comprised of your peers based on your needs, their skills, and everyoneâs engagement. In addition, one of the early assignments will be for each team to find one or two domain experts to serve on their board for the duration of the class. One of the requirements in this class is to serve on another teamâs board. As we go, we will refine board membership based on peer reviews and demonstrated effort. We will optimize this class for entrepreneurs willing to invest the time and energy to help themselves and others.', 'https://novoed.com/boardroom', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/dTaqyshR1gU?vq=auto&rel=0&showinfo=0&autohide=1&wmode=transparent&origin=https://novoed.com', '2013-10-08', 74, '', '', 'NovoEd', 249, 'English', 'yes', '', '2015-11-24 23:09:29'),
(3465, 'The Chemistry of Life', 'EdX keeps courses open for enrollment after they end to allow learners to explore content and continue learning.', 'EdX keeps courses open for enrollment after they end to allow learners to explore content and continue learning. All features and materials may not be all available. Check back often to see when new course start dates are announced.  Chemistry and biology are traditionally taught as separate subjects at the high school level, where students memorize fundamental scientific principles that are universally accepted. However, at the university level and in industry, we learn that science is not as simple as we once thought. We are constantly confronted by questions about the unknown and required to use creative, integrated approaches to solve these problems. By bringing together knowledge from multidisciplinary fields, we are empowered with the ability to generate new ideas. The goal of this course is to develop skills for generating new ideas at the interface between chemistry and biology by analyzing pioneering studies. When should I register? Registration will be open throughout the course. However, if a learner wants to receive a certificate, he/she should register by the end of April. ', 'https://edx.org/course/chemistry-life-kyotoux-001x-0', 'http://www.youtube.com/v/yw2u3191whY?version=3&amp;autohide=1', '2015-11-24', 105, 'https://www.edx.org/sites/default/files/styles/course_video_banner/public/course/image/featured-card/ku_chem_378x225.jpg?itok=G0CQORpC', 'Biology & Life Sciences', 'edX', 0, 'English', 'yes', 'KyotoUx', '2015-11-24 23:09:30'),
(3466, 'The Finance of Retirement & Pensions', 'In this eight-week course, you will learn the financial concepts behind sound retirement plan investment and pension fund management.', 'In this eight-week course, you will learn the financial concepts behind sound retirement plan investment and pension fund management. Course participants will become more informed decision makers about their own portfolios, and be equipped to evaluate economic policy discussions that surround public pensions. The course begins with the principles of financial economics, such as the distribution of outcomes when investing in stocks, bonds, or annuities. These serve as the building blocks for an understanding of different retirement strategies that can help you improve your asset allocation. Finally, the course applies these principles to government programs and policies.', 'https://novoed.com/rauh-finance', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/e8d6GPryYWQ?vq=auto&rel=0&showinfo=0&autohide=1&wmode=transparent&origin=https://novoed.com', '2013-10-15', 60, '', '', 'NovoEd', -1, 'English', 'no', 'Stanford Graduate School of Business', '2015-11-24 23:09:29');
