(4091, 'Analytical Chemistry / Instrumental Analysis', 'If chemistry is the science of stuff, then analytical chemistry answers the question: what is it? And how much of it do you have? This course teaches how to do this with instrumental analysis! ', 'If chemistry is the science of stuff, then analytical chemistry answers the question: what is it? And how much of it do you have? This course teaches how to do this with instrumental analysis! ', 'https://class.coursera.org/analyticalchem-003/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rWyUwM-GwgE', '2015-11-18', 8, 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/coursera/topics/analyticalchem/large-icon.png', 'Chemistry,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Rice University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
(4093, 'Nanotechnology: The Basics', 'Nanotechnology is an emerging area that engages almost every technical discipline â from chemistry to computer science â in the study and application of extremely tiny materials. Â This short course allows any technically savvy person to go one layer beyond the surface of this broad topic to see the real substance behind the very small.', 'Nanotechnology is an emerging area that engages almost every technical discipline â from chemistry to computer science â in the study and application of extremely tiny materials. Â This short course allows any technically savvy person to go one layer beyond the surface of this broad topic to see the real substance behind the very small.', 'https://class.coursera.org/nanotech-001/', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xg-EbtAxPzw', '2013-11-11', 9, 'https://s3.amazonaws.com/coursera/topics/nanotech/large-icon.png', 'Health & Society,Physical & Earth Sciences,Biology & Life Sciences,Engineering,Physics,Chemistry,', 'Coursera', 0, 'English', 'no', 'Rice University,', '2015-11-18 00:00:00'),
